  questionText: The fuse wire should have_______.
  referenceImage: {fileID: 0}
  explanationText: A fuse wire should have a high resistance so that a lot of heat
    is generated and it is easier for the fuse wire to reach its melting point. Also,
    a fuse wire should have a low melting point so that it can melt easily.
  options:
  - high melting point and high resistance
  - low melting point and low resistance
  - low melting point and high resistance
  - high melting point and low resistance
